Quickstrike:




Quickstrike paused. He still had duties to do. He was getting tired of 
waiting for the stasis pod to arrive. He sighed, and opened his comm-link to 
Stingra, who he nearly forgot. He knew she and someone else was out there. 
"Hey, ya find any pods yet? We's got some new bots comin' in, and ah's ain't 
hear from y'all."
